      "content": "but it's not just a setback. it's the whole thing. the person everyone respected, the person i thought i was... that person was a ghost. i look in the mirror and there's nothing there because the work was everything. without the research, i'm just a hollow shell. i feel like i've been living a life that doesn't belong to me, and now that the truth is out, there's no reason to keep up the act.",
